  "title": "refactor: remove hogan.js",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\n[FX-3031](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3031)\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n- Templates should be functions or strings. Functions returning simple strings and simple strings directly work, if it returns a string with HTML tags these will be escaped by Preact.\r\n  - Updated all default templates and tests accordingly.\r\n- Took the opportunity to remove `bindEvent` as it was linked to templates.\r\n- Still kept the `Template` component as templates are not valid components, they take 2 arguments.\r\n- Removed hogan dependencies\r\n\r\n[FX-3031]: https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-3031?atlOrigin=eyJpIjoiNWRkNTljNzYxNjVmNDY3MDlhMDU5Y2ZhYzA5YTRkZjUiLCJwIjoiZ2l0aHViLWNvbS1KU1cifQ",
